author: hwright
msg: Call the receiver directly for 'svn info' operations.
* subversion/svn/info-cmd.c
(print_info_xml, print_info): Add a baton argument, and note that these now
implement the svn_info_receiver_t callback.
(info_receiver): Remove.
(svn_cl__info): Decide which receiver to use once, and use a local variable
to reference that receiver in the call to svn_client_info().

author: hwright
msg: Condense code by removing redundant invocations of svn_client_blame3().  This
is similar to what r23295 did for proplist.
* subversion/svn/blame-cmd.c
(svn_cl__blame): Use a local variable for the svn_client_blame_receiver_t
which is passed to svn_client_blame3().
